4
00:01:08,735 --> 00:01:09,570
Who are you?

5
00:01:17,202 --> 00:01:18,620
<i><font color="white">I learned that</font></i>

6
00:01:19,454 --> 00:01:21,456
<i><font color="white">one day is all it takes</font></i>

7
00:01:23,709 --> 00:01:24,960
<i><font color="white">for my entire life</font></i>

8
00:01:26,712 --> 00:01:29,172
<i><font color="white">to be turned upside down.</font></i>

9
00:01:31,341 --> 00:01:32,342
<i><font color="white">I learned that…</font></i>

10
00:01:32,884 --> 00:01:33,969
Hi.

11
00:01:34,469 --> 00:01:35,512
Long time no see.

12
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:38,932
<i><font color="white">…for the first time 20 years ago.</font></i>

13
00:01:39,016 --> 00:01:41,018
ON DUTY FOR YOUR SAFETY AND HAPPINESS
YOUNGSAN POLICE STATION

14
00:01:44,229 --> 00:01:45,272
Hey, kid.

15
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:47,316
Is something wrong?

16
00:01:47,816 --> 00:01:48,775
Do you need help?

17
00:01:54,323 --> 00:01:55,741
