Don't be mistaken.

683
00:55:59,273 --> 00:56:01,608
It's not like I actually liked you.

684
00:56:02,734 --> 00:56:05,237
If you needed money,
you should have just said so.

685
00:56:06,530 --> 00:56:07,990
You pathetic orphan.

686
00:56:23,547 --> 00:56:26,800
JIN SEUNG-HO OF YOUNGSAN HIGH SCHOOL
ACCEPTED TO SNU SCHOOL OF LAW

687
00:56:28,552 --> 00:56:31,513
<i><font color="white">But can you just pretend
that you briefly went out</font></i>

688
00:56:32,014 --> 00:56:33,932
<i><font color="white">with a law student
from Seoul National University?</font></i>

689
00:56:40,480 --> 00:56:41,315
Jin Seung-ho.

690
00:56:51,867 --> 00:56:53,452
<i><font color="white">Twenty years ago,</font></i>

691
00:56:56,371 --> 00:56:57,873
<i><font color="white">the day my life was</font></i>

692
00:56:58,749 --> 00:57:01,251
<i><font color="white">turned upside down
for the very first time…</font></i>

693
00:57:04,588 --> 00:57:05,797
You killed him.

694
00:57:07,257 --> 00:57:08,342
You murderer.

695
00:57:13,555 --> 00:57:16,433
My Seung-ho…

696
00:57:19,102 --> 00:57:22,856
My poor baby…

697
00:57:25,025 --> 00:57:29,196
My goodness, Seung-ho…

698
00:57:33,992 --> 00:57:35,786
JIN SEUNG-HO OF YOUNGSAN HIGH SCHOOL
ACCEPTED TO SNU SCHOOL OF LAW

699
00:57:39,206 --> 00:57:41,833
YOUNGSAN TO GANGNAM

700
00:57:45,629 --> 00:57:47,589
<i><font color="white">The only thing I could do…</font></i>

701
00:57:52,010 --> 00:57:53,762
<i><font color="white">was to run away.</font></i>

702
00:57:57,891 --> 00:58:00,686
KO JI-SEOP'S WIFE CAUSES
BIGGEST CRISIS OF HIS CAREER

703
00:58:02,813 --> 00:58:04,439
<i><font color="white">I never thought I would come back.</font></i>

704
00:58:41,268 --> 00:58:43,520
ILHWADANG

705
00:58:50,861 --> 00:58:51,945
There she is.

706
00:59:06,043 --> 00:59:07,252
Honey.

707
00:59:17,763 --> 00:59:18,638
You made it.

708
00:59:52,589 --> 00:59:55,467
TROLLEY

709
00:59:55,550 --> 00:59:57,469
<i><font color="white">This is between us. My husband--</font></i>

710
00:59:57,552 --> 01:00:01,181
<i><font color="white">Your husband is an assemblyman, no less,
and the elections are coming up.</font></i>

711
01:00:01,264 --> 01:00:04,059
<i><font color="white">Should I put up banners
and hand out fliers about what you did?</font></i>

712
01:00:04,142 --> 01:00:07,479
<i><font color="white">My wife will not have any influence
over my political activities.</font></i>

713
01:00:07,562 --> 01:00:09,981
I know it's too late,
but I have to do something.

714
01:00:10,065 --> 01:00:11,358
<i><font color="white">Let's do one thing at a time, shall we?</font></i>

715
01:00:11,441 --> 01:00:12,859
<i><font color="white">Why did she have to get involved?</font></i>

716
01:00:12,943 --> 01:00:14,820
<i><font color="white">You. Can you take responsibility?</font></i>

717
01:00:14,903 --> 01:00:16,571
<i><font color="white">You're one to talk.</font></i>

718
01:00:16,655 --> 01:00:18,573
<i><font color="white">Why do you want to know?</font></i>

719
01:00:18,657 --> 01:00:20,659
<i><font color="white">Is there something you find suspicious?</font></i>

720
01:00:20,742 --> 01:00:25,622
